OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FLargely dry
OL,6,Fwith clear spells through the evening
OL,7,Fand overnight, but with the odd shower
OL,8,Ffeeding in from the west at times.
OL,9,FOccasionally blustery southwest winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,CFriday:FLargely dry morning with
OL,12,Fbright or sunny spells, though with
OL,13,Fthe chance of the odd shower. Cloudier
OL,14,Fin the afternoon with some evening
OL,15,Frain. A bit cooler than recent days.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
