OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FCloudy
OL,6,FSaturday morning with some outbreaks
OL,7,Fof rain, becoming drier and brighter
OL,8,Flater. Cloudy and windy at times with
OL,9,Foccasional spells of rain on Sunday
OL,10,Fand Monday.
